# WhyzeD Programming Language (Zed)
# Stage 2: Self-Reflective Core

# 1. Initialize the Empire Environment
Set System_Active 1
Set Security_Level 100

# 2. Logic to handle a 'Build' request
# (This simulates the parser looking at a command)
Set Input_Command 1
Compare Input_Command 1

# 3. If the command is valid, we signal the Ready state
Show System_Active
Show Security_Level
